snippet.title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt || GAME OF THE YEAR Trailer
snippet.description:
The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt -- Game of the Year Edition launches on 30.08.2016. 

The winner of over 800 awards, including more than 250 game of the year awards, both critically acclaimed expansion packs and all additional content ever released -- now available in one, epic package. Search for the child of prophecy in Wild Hunt, deal with the devil in Hearts of Stone and discover a terrifying secret of the beautiful region of Toussaint in Blood and Wine. 

Visit buy.thewitcher.com to order your copy!

In select territories and sales channels the game will be available as The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Complete Edition.

For more information about The Witcher visit:
Facebook: https://www.fb.com/thewitcher
Twitter: https://twitter.com/witchergame
Homepage: http://thewitcher.com/witcher3
Instagram: https://instagram.com/cdpred
